description:
Mariela Sametband and Guillermo “El Peque” Barrionuevo dance “Paciencia” played live by Solo Tango Orquesta, sung by Sebastián Arce, at the Sultans of Istanbul Tango Festival 2016 in Istanbul, Turkey.
